    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Possible, it would avoid cases in which an InstantSearch component is wrapped inside a form. However, this should also be fine if we do `preventDefault` inside each of the default event listeners. We can do that in a breaking change, but without breaking the DOM.\r\n\r\nIn which places do we have buttons? ",
